name: Faroe  v1.2.0
body:
### Changes

* updated [janmayen](https://github.com/52North/janmayen) to `v1.1.0`
* updated [parent pom](https://github.com/52North/maven-parents) to `v7`

This release is available on Maven Central:

```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.n52.faroe</groupId>
    <artifactId>faroe</artifactId>
    <version>1.2.0</version>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.n52.faroe</groupId>
    <artifactId>faroe-json</artifactId>
    <version>1.2.0</version>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.n52.faroe</groupId>
    <artifactId>faroe-annotations</artifactId>
    <version>1.2.0</version>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.n52.faroe</groupId>
    <artifactId>faroe-utils</artifactId>
    <version>1.2.0</version>
</dependency>
```
